Version 0.3.14, 2026-04-26
New features:
- Documented project for PHP 7.4+ / MySQL 8, Docker dev stack, and security in README, AGENTS, SECURITY, and .agent skills.
- Replaced ext/mysql with mysqli; prepared statements for high-risk web/admin SQL (find-chat, find-players, user admin, parser).
Changes and bugfixes:
- Hardened redirects and sessions; chat/player search and admin user flows use bound parameters; schema tweaks for MySQL 8 (utf8mb4).
- Bundled static docs converted to Markdown under src/doc/en/; added Content-Security-Policy operator notes in SECURITY.md.
